We can'’t win them all.

16:04.650 --> 16:06.570
[laughter and chattering]

16:11.700 --> 16:13.790
[cell phone chimes]

16:26.240 --> 16:28.200
Charley, good to see you.

16:28.240 --> 16:29.640
And you.

16:29.680 --> 16:31.250
Good to have you back
in town, Frances.

16:31.290 --> 16:32.990
Aw.

16:34.470 --> 16:37.510
