in a dangerous world.

26:13.180 --> 26:15.440
From the chapter
"Buried Memories."

26:18.790 --> 26:21.620
"I loved my father
beyond measure,

26:21.660 --> 26:24.620
and I learned to love
whatever he loved,

26:24.670 --> 26:29.370
so any time we spent together
would become glorious time.

26:29.410 --> 26:31.190
Often that meant
just the two of us,

26:31.240 --> 26:33.630
