27:24.380 --> 27:26.810
I liked to wander
through the cane at night.

27:26.860 --> 27:29.510
I loved the richness
of the land.

27:29.560 --> 27:34.000
It was me alone
and safe in my world.

27:35.870 --> 27:39.130
It was about a week after
that aborted fishing trip.

27:39.170 --> 27:41.440
I was out in the night
